   Yadkin County Facts:
     * Total Land Area: 336 square miles
     * County Population: 34,955
     * Population Density per Square Mile: 104
     * County Tax Rate: $0.64 per  $100 valuation
     * County Seat: Yadkinville, NC
     * Five Municipalities:

             Yadkinville, Jonesville, Boonville,
              East Bend and Arlington
   County Manager:  Cecil Wood
   County Attorney:  James Graham
   Finance Officer:    Geraldine Nance
   Yadkin County Administration Building:
     * Mailing Address:  P.O. Box 146, Yadkinville, NC 27055
     * Location:  217 E. Willow Street
     * Open to the Public:  8:00 am-5:00 pm

            Monday thru Friday
     * Telephone: (336)679-4200
     * Number of  Fulltime Employees: 221
     * Number of Departments: 18

